{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We suffered together the suffering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ade, Kamerad, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I feel sorry for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this parting [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] is very difficult for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's heavy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You were so good for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You gave me much courage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And now we will never see each other again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, oddly enough, I wrote under there the date that my father was transported.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So, I mean, that's not one of the lighter songs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I could-- I know the melody, but I don't trust myself to sing it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't think I'll ever forget the melody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I think probably what made it-- the-- my father's death especially difficult is that we didn't talk about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My mother and I didn't share it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It wasn't cried about.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My grandfather, who I was very attached to, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] it was like a total disappearance rather than a cut.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I think that it, therefore, it just lingered longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] I-- apparently from-- from what I reread-- I-- I did a lot of searching yesterday-- accepted, at one level, that my father had died in 1947.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I wouldn't say Kaddish for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I didn't say Kaddish for him till [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] probably 20 years later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I just-- I just couldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, now I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- so there was-- there-- there is a certain-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] that it didn't really end.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It just simmered on and on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this whole camp period, I mean, not talking about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we moved to America, nobody knew about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
